,"sentences":[{"en":"Follow TechRadar on Google News and add us as a preferred source to get our expert news, reviews, and opinion in your feeds.","zh":"在 Google 新闻上关注 TechRadar，并将我们添加为首选来源，以便在您的 Feed 中获取我们的专家新闻、评论和意见。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Sign up for breaking news, reviews, opinion, top tech deals, and more.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Sign up for breaking news, reviews, opinion, top tech deals, and more.","zh":"订阅突发新闻、评论、观点、顶级技术交易等。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Matt is TechRadar's Managing Editor for Entertainment, meaning he's in charge of persuading our team of writers and reviewers to watch the latest TV shows and movies on gorgeous TVs and listen to fantastic speakers and headphones. It's a tough task, as you can imagine. Matt has over a decade of experience in tech publishing, and previously ran the TV &amp; audio coverage for our colleagues at T3.com, and before that he edited T3 magazine. During his career, he's also contributed to places as varied as Creative Bloq, PC Gamer, PetsRadar, MacLife, and Edge. TV and movie nerdism is his speciality, and he goes to the cinema three times a week. He's always happy to explain the virtues of Dolby Vision over a drink, but he might need to use props, like he's explaining the offside rule.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Matt is TechRadar's Managing Editor for Entertainment, meaning he's in charge of persuading our team of writers and reviewers to watch the latest TV shows and movies on gorgeous TVs and listen to fantastic speakers and headphones.","zh":"马特是 TechRadar 的娱乐总编辑，这意味着他负责说服我们的作家和评论家团队在华丽的电视上观看最新的电视节目和电影，并聆听出色的扬声器和耳机。"},{"en":"It's a tough task, as you can imagine.","zh":"正如您可以想象的那样，这是一项艰巨的任务。"},{"en":"Matt has over a decade of experience in tech publishing, and previously ran the TV & audio coverage for our colleagues at T3.com, and before that he edited T3 magazine.","zh":"Matt 在科技出版方面拥有十多年的经验，之前曾为 T3.com 的同事负责电视和音频报道，在此之前他还编辑过 T3 杂志。"},{"en":"During his career, he's also contributed to places as varied as Creative Bloq, PC Gamer, PetsRadar, MacLife, and Edge.","zh":"在他的职业生涯中，他还为 Creative Bloq、PC Gamer、PetsRadar、MacLife 和 Edge 等多个领域做出了贡献。"},{"en":"TV and movie nerdism is his speciality, and he goes to the cinema three times a week.","zh":"电视和电影书呆子是他的专长，他每周去电影院三次。"},{"en":"He's always happy to explain the virtues of Dolby Vision over a drink, but he might need to use props, like he's explaining the offside rule.","zh":"他总是很乐意边喝酒边解释杜比视界的优点，但他可能需要使用道具，就像他解释越位规则一样。"}]}],"translated":true,"content_html_zh":"<div class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><div id=\"content\" data-widget-type=\"contentparsed\">\n<section>\n<div>\n<figure>\n<picture data-new-v2-image=\"true\">\n<source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC-2560-80.jpg.webp 2560w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC-1440-80.jpg.webp 1440w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC-1200-80.jpg.webp 1200w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC-970-80.jpg.webp 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC-750-80.jpg.webp 750w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC-650-80.jpg.webp 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC-480-80.jpg.webp 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"100vw\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC.jpg\" alt=\"A collage image consisting of someone holding The Power of the Dog on Criterion 4K Blu-ray, Body Heat on Criterion 4K Blu-ray, and a Blu-ray player with 3:10 to Yuma Criterion 4K Blu-ray in its tray\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC-2560-80.jpg 2560w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC-1920-80.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC-1440-80.jpg 1440w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC-1200-80.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC-750-80.jpg 750w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"100vw\" data-new-v2-image=\"true\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zLwopfrFkgzoqd6GCdLWHC.jpg\" data-pin-nopin=\"true\" fetchpriority=\"high\" data-component-name=\"Image\">\n</picture>\n<figcaption>（图片来源：未来）</figcaption>\n</figure></div>\n<div id=\"article-body\">\n\n<p id=\"elk-5e40ea84-867d-11f1-b149-95265fd61e4b\">对于 4K 蓝光粉丝来说，这是个好消息：Barnes &amp; Noble 仍在进行 Criterion Collections 光盘的巨额半价促销，亚马逊也有一些相同的折扣。 更令人关注的消息是：特卖将于 7 月 26 日结束，因此您只剩下几天时间来购买一些新光盘！</p><p>• 查看 Barnes &amp; Noble 的完整 Criterion 促销活动• 查看 Amazon 的 Criterion 促销活动</p><p>在 Barnes &amp; Noble，绝对所有商品都是半价，这让事情变得简单（而且非常便宜）。 在亚马逊，不少光盘是半价，但有些折扣比 B&amp;N 还要小（或者根本没有折扣）。 但我也把这次销售也包括在内，因为很多人喜欢从亚马逊开始，以方便起见。</p><p>显然，有大量的商品可供选择，因此您最好的选择是直接浏览完整的促销活动，但我挑选了 12 个我认为特别诱人的选项。 如果您还没有 4K 蓝光播放器，请不要忘记查看我们的最佳 4K 蓝光播放器指南，所有内容均经过我们的测试！</p><h2 id=\"criterion-4k-blu-ray-sale-quick-links-3\">Criterion 4K 蓝光销售 — 快速链接</h2><ul id=\"elk-5e40ec50-867d-11f1-99de-df272ab35fef\"><li>查看 Barnes &amp; Noble 的完整 Criterion 促销活动</li><li>查看亚马逊 Criterion 的完整促销</li></ul><h3 id=\"section-criterion-4k-blu-ray-sale-12-titles-i-d-recommend\">Criterion 4K 蓝光特卖：我推荐的 12 部影片</h3><hr id=\"elk-5e40f164-867d-11f1-8ed5-d56e9d0e9000\"><ul id=\"elk-5e40f1be-867d-11f1-92fe-9f30be6a9727\"><li>查看亚马逊 Criterion 的完整促销</li><li>查看 Barnes &amp; Noble 的完整 Criterion 促销活动</li></ul><div data-component-name=\"Slice:Person\" id=\"elk-5e40f218-867d-11f1-a092-0bf5eb9fb58f\">\n<figure>\n<div>\n<picture data-new-v2-image=\"true\">\n<source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/s6vZHBgGGnnZ8YFREg4bbT-140-80.jpg.webp 140w\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/s6vZHBgGGnnZ8YFREg4bbT.jpg\" alt=\"Panasonic DP-UB20 square\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/s6vZHBgGGnnZ8YFREg4bbT-140-80.jpg 140w\" loading=\"lazy\" data-new-v2-image=\"true\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/s6vZHBgGGnnZ8YFREg4bbT.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/s6vZHBgGGnnZ8YFREg4bbT.jpg\" data-pin-nopin=\"true\" data-normal=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/s6vZHBgGGnnZ8YFREg4bbT.jpg\" data-slice-image=\"true\">\n</picture>\n</div>\n</figure>\n</div><hr id=\"elk-5e40f27c-867d-11f1-bdd6-33ab883f6769\"><a href=\"https://news.google.com/publications/CAAqKAgKIiJDQklTRXdnTWFnOEtEWFJsWTJoeVlXUmhjaTVqYjIwb0FBUAE?hl=en-GB&gl=GB&ceid=GB%3Aen\" target=\"_blank\" id=\"elk-5e40f2d6-867d-11f1-8717-a1c65b77cd36\" data-url=\"https://news.google.com/publications/CAAqKAgKIiJDQklTRXdnTWFnOEtEWFJsWTJoeVlXUmhjaTVqYjIwb0FBUAE?hl=en-GB&gl=GB&ceid=GB%3Aen\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" data-hl-processed=\"none\"><figure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"><div><p> <picture data-new-v2-image=\"true\">\n<source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/diM9tpwF2Lz85R8q85CT78-676-80.jpg.webp 2560w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/diM9tpwF2Lz85R8q85CT78-676-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/diM9tpwF2Lz85R8q85CT78-676-80.jpg.webp 1440w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/diM9tpwF2Lz85R8q85CT78-676-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/diM9tpwF2Lz85R8q85CT78-676-80.jpg.webp 1200w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/diM9tpwF2Lz85R8q85CT78-676-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/diM9tpwF2Lz85R8q85CT78-676-80.jpg.webp 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/diM9tpwF2Lz85R8q85CT78-650-80.jpg.webp 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/diM9tpwF2Lz85R8q85CT78-480-80.jpg.webp 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/diM9tpwF2Lz85R8q85CT78-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"100vw\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/diM9tpwF2Lz85R8q85CT78.jpg\" alt=\"Google logo on a black background next to text reading 'Click to follow TechRadar'\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/diM9tpwF2Lz85R8q85CT78-676-80.jpg 2560w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/diM9tpwF2Lz85R8q85CT78-676-80.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/diM9tpwF2Lz85R8q85CT78-676-80.jpg 1440w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/diM9tpwF2Lz85R8q85CT78-676-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/diM9tpwF2Lz85R8q85CT78-676-80.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/diM9tpwF2Lz85R8q85CT78-676-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/diM9tpwF2Lz85R8q85CT78-676-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/diM9tpwF2Lz85R8q85CT78-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/diM9tpwF2Lz85R8q85CT78-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/diM9tpwF2Lz85R8q85CT78-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\" data-new-v2-image=\"true\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/diM9tpwF2Lz85R8q85CT78.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/diM9tpwF2Lz85R8q85CT78.jpg\">\n</picture></p></div></figure></a><p id=\"elk-5e40f330-867d-11f1-aa75-a11837dd0b37\">在 Google 新闻上关注 TechRadar，并将我们添加为首选来源，以便在您的 Feed 中获取我们的专家新闻、评论和意见。</p>\n</div>\n\n<div data-hydrate=\"true\" id=\"slice-container-newsletterForm-articleInbodyContent-nuLTijq3c6UmFibEwM82nJ\"><section><p>订阅突发新闻、评论、观点、顶级技术交易等。</p></section></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-hydrate=\"true\" id=\"slice-container-authorBio-nuLTijq3c6UmFibEwM82nJ\"><p>马特是 TechRadar 的娱乐总编辑，这意味着他负责说服我们的作家和评论家团队在华丽的电视上观看最新的电视节目和电影，并聆听出色的扬声器和耳机。 正如您可以想象的那样，这是一项艰巨的任务。 Matt 在科技出版方面拥有十多年的经验，之前曾为 T3.com 的同事负责电视和音频报道，在此之前他还编辑过 T3 杂志。 在他的职业生涯中，他还为 Creative Bloq、PC Gamer、PetsRadar、MacLife 和 Edge 等多个领域做出了贡献。 电视和电影书呆子是他的专长，他每周去电影院三次。 他总是很乐意边喝酒边解释杜比视界的优点，但他可能需要使用道具，就像他解释越位规则一样。</p></div>\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n</div></div>"}